<doc id="1052953" wikidata="Q104057" url="?curid=1052953" title="Collio, Lombardy">
<text>Collio (Brescian: ) is a town and &quot;comune&quot; in the province of Brescia, in Lombardy, Italy. Neighbouring communes are Bagolino, Bienno, Bovegno, Lavenone, Marmentino, Pertica Alta and Pertica Bassa.

==Twin towns==
Collio is twinned with:

* Castroreale, Italy
* Gonnesa, Italy

