<text>Cologne (Brescian: ) is a town and &quot;commune&quot; in the province of Brescia, in Lombardy. Cologne is located in Franciacorta at the foot of Monte Orfano. Neighbouring communes are Coccaglio, Erbusco, Palazzolo sull&#x27;Oglio and Chiari.

